===Noun===
'''epic'''
# an [[extended]] [[narrative]] [[poem]] in elevated or dignified language, [[celebrating]] the [[feat]]s of a [[legendary]] or traditional [[hero]]
#:''The Icelandic '''epic''' took all night to recite.''
# a [[series]] of [[event]]s considered [[appropriate]] to an epic
#:''The book was an '''epic''' in four volumes.''

